Package it.polimi.ingsw.view.implementation.gui.widget

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    BaseProductionWidget
    Widget that lets the player perform a base production.
    ChatWidget
    Widget that represents the chat.
    DeckWidget
    Widget that represents the deck of development cards.
    DepositWidget
    Widget that represents a deposit.
    DevelopmentCardWidget
    Widget that represents a development card.
    DevelopmentSlotsWidget
    Widget that shows the stacks of development cards owned by the player.
    EndGameWidget
    Widget that shows the rank when a game ends.
    FaithTrackWidget
    Widget that represents the faith track of a player.
    LeaderCardWidget
    Widget that represents a leader card.
    LeaderDisplayWidget
    Widget that shows the leader cards possessed by a player.
    LeaderSelectionWidget
    Widget that is used at the beginning of the match to let the player decide which leader cards to keep and, optionally, which resources to take.
    MarketResultsWidget
    Widget that represents the resources drawn by a player from the market, waiting to be stored.
    MarketWidget
    Widget that models the market.
    MusicButtonWidget
    Widget for the button to play/stop background music.
    PlayerBoardWidget
    Main widget that represents a player board.
    ProductionWidget
    Widget to create and queue a production.
    StrongBoxWidget
    Widget for displaying the strongbox of a Player.
